WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.215 --> 00:00:10.119
MOBILE SUIT GUNDAM GQUUUUUUX

2
00:00:10.119 --> 00:00:10.219
MOBILE SUIT GUNDAM GQUUUUUUX

3
00:00:50.551 --> 00:00:55.347
Perintah sekatan! Kawalan Izuma Side 6
keluarkan isyarat jangan masuk.

4
00:00:56.140 --> 00:00:59.643
Ada mobile suit penjual sekerap
memasuki laluan penerbangan kita.

5
00:01:00.644 --> 00:01:04.648
Sebab itu saya bantah kita jual
mobile suit kepada orang awam.

6
00:01:05.149 --> 00:01:07.026
Lantaklah! Biar mereka menghampiri.

7
00:01:08.152 --> 00:01:12.448
Tapi kunci pemasang dah dikeluarkan.
Mereka tak boleh guna senjata.

8
00:01:13.115 --> 00:01:14.116
Mestilah tak boleh!

9
00:01:15.201 --> 00:01:16.994
Adukan kepada Side 6.

10
00:01:17.495 --> 00:01:18.496
Baik.

11
00:01:18.579 --> 00:01:21.707
Ini peluang kerja
untuk saki-baki Tentera Persekutuan.

12
00:01:22.917 --> 00:01:24.710
Pihak yang menang pun
kena bertanggungjawab.

13
00:01:26.879 --> 00:01:29.215
Ini kejahatan yang perlu demi keamanan.

14
00:01:29.298 --> 00:01:33.052
Saya faham. tapi Side 6 juga
negara berdaulat.

15
00:01:33.135 --> 00:01:35.846
Zeon tak ada kewajipan untuk jaga mereka.

16
00:01:37.932 --> 00:01:40.935
Ada masalah. Komander Challia Bull?

17
00:01:42.353 --> 00:01:43.354
Gundam.

18
00:01:44.146 --> 00:01:47.817
-Macam mana tuan tahu?
-Itu gerak hati orang dari Musytari?

19
00:01:49.401 --> 00:01:50.402
Tak syak lagi…

20
00:01:51.695 --> 00:01:52.947
itu Gundam Merah.

21
00:01:54.907 --> 00:01:56.242
Saya hilang jejak sasaran.

22
00:01:56.742 --> 00:01:59.036
Ke mana awak pergi?

23
00:02:05.751 --> 00:02:07.711
Tak guna! Mav saya terbunuh!

24
00:02:09.213 --> 00:02:10.214
Pantasnya!

25
00:02:11.799 --> 00:02:13.175
Apa benda itu?

26
00:02:22.434 --> 00:02:23.853
"Gundam Merah."

27
00:02:26.188 --> 00:02:27.565
Tidak Dikenali
Mari pergi ke Permulaan.

28
00:02:27.648 --> 00:02:28.649
Siapa ini?

29
00:02:28.732 --> 00:02:31.318
Apa ini? Orang mengusik?

30
00:02:35.447 --> 00:02:37.908
Terima kasih kerana
menggunakan Stesen Camden hari ini.

31
00:02:37.992 --> 00:02:39.410
KHIDMAT LALUAN
LINGKARAN CL6 TERGENDALA

32
00:02:39.493 --> 00:02:40.911
DISEBABKAN SIASATAN POLIS.

33
00:02:44.415 --> 00:02:46.792
Hei. awak! Berhenti!

34
00:02:47.376 --> 00:02:50.296
Jangan lari! Hei. tunggu!

35
00:02:51.297 --> 00:02:54.133
Hei. awak! Saya kata berhenti!

36
00:03:06.520 --> 00:03:07.521
Hei. tunggu!

37
00:03:07.605 --> 00:03:08.898
Tepilah!

38
00:03:09.565 --> 00:03:11.358
Tunggu! Saya kata berhenti!

39
00:03:14.778 --> 00:03:17.698
Sebuah koloni angkasa berdiameter 6.4 km

40
00:03:17.781 --> 00:03:21.285
-menghasilkan graviti putaran 1G…
-Siapa itu? Dia buat apa?

41
00:03:21.368 --> 00:03:24.371
-…dengan berputar setiap 113.5 saat.
-Amate. turun! Bahaya!

42
00:03:24.455 --> 00:03:27.291
Daya yang menekan kami
ke tanah ini bukan graviti sebenar.

43
00:03:27.374 --> 00:03:28.834
Nampak seluar dalam awak!

44
00:03:30.544 --> 00:03:34.173
Syurga bukan di atas.
tapi di bawah kaki kami.

45
00:03:34.715 --> 00:03:40.387
Orang yang lahir di koloni macam kami
tak kenal graviti atau langit sebenar.

46
00:03:48.771 --> 00:03:51.774
Apatah lagi laut sebenar.

47
00:04:00.491 --> 00:04:05.621
Kami berusaha untuk memastikan
keselamatan pengguna Stesen Camden

48
00:04:05.704 --> 00:04:09.124
dengan bekerjasama dengan polis tentera
untuk membasmi aktiviti haram.

49
00:04:09.625 --> 00:04:11.669
-Terima kasih kerana memahami.
-Apa ini?

50
00:04:16.757 --> 00:04:18.842
Tak mungkin ini bom.

51
00:04:19.343 --> 00:04:20.511
Bukan?

52
00:04:24.223 --> 00:04:27.518
FOOLYPEDIA
Ensiklopedia Dikemas Kini

53
00:04:30.104 --> 00:04:31.772
"Kunci pemasang"?

54
00:04:32.690 --> 00:04:36.402
Untuk komputer tempur mobile suit?

55
00:04:38.362 --> 00:04:41.407
Ini barang seludup haram!

56
00:04:55.045 --> 00:04:56.922
Sasaran menuju ke medan sekerap selatan.

57
00:04:57.006 --> 00:05:00.175
Polis rusuhan perisai.
ambil alih pengejaran.

58
00:05:00.259 --> 00:05:03.137
Saya ulang. sasaran menuju
ke medan sekerap selatan.

59
00:05:03.220 --> 00:05:06.265
Polis rusuhan perisai.
ambil alih pengejaran.

60
00:05:07.182 --> 00:05:10.310
Apa benda yang sasaran lukis ini?

61
00:05:11.020 --> 00:05:12.146
Peduli apa?

62
00:05:12.229 --> 00:05:13.313
Kejar mereka!

63
00:05:16.442 --> 00:05:18.235
Sasaran masih melarikan diri.

64
00:05:18.861 --> 00:05:22.114
MP Side 6 masih belum
berjaya menangkap sasaran.

65
00:05:22.197 --> 00:05:25.325
Biar betul. Betulkah dia Komet Merah?

66
00:05:25.409 --> 00:05:28.620
Dah ramai orang menyamar jadi Kapten Char.

67
00:05:29.246 --> 00:05:30.998
Mesti yang ini pun menyamar.

68
00:05:32.207 --> 00:05:35.878
Ensain Comoli. saya pasti awak pun
pernah dengar tentang asal usul kapten.

69
00:05:36.754 --> 00:05:40.174
Ada khabar angin kata dia satu-satunya
anak Zeon Deikun yang terselamat.

70
00:05:40.257 --> 00:05:42.509
Saya tahu dia kawan tuan.

71
00:05:42.593 --> 00:05:46.305
Saya dengar dia Mav tuan.
tapi itu cuma kata orang.

72
00:05:46.388 --> 00:05:47.806
Saya tak percaya.

73
00:05:48.849 --> 00:05:52.394
Tapi Puan Yang Terutama Kycilia
tak rasa begitu.

74
00:05:52.478 --> 00:05:54.646
Kami ke sini untuk menyiasat.

75
00:05:55.481 --> 00:05:57.524
Leftenan Kowal.
macam mana Gundam GQuuuuuuX?

76
00:05:58.525 --> 00:06:01.820
Ensain Xavier
sedang berlatih bertukar mesin.

77
00:06:03.322 --> 00:06:06.116
Kita akan gunakan
kunci pengaktifan Psycommu Omega.

78
00:06:06.617 --> 00:06:07.868
Nanti dulu!

79
00:06:07.951 --> 00:06:10.746
Kita belum dapat kelulusan Granada!

80
00:06:10.829 --> 00:06:15.334
Bukankah mereka pinjamkan kita mobile suit
dengan syarat Psycommu tak digunakan?

81
00:06:15.959 --> 00:06:20.172
Psycommu Omega tak pernah
digunakan dalam pertempuran sebenar!

82
00:06:20.672 --> 00:06:23.675
Kalau ia hilang kawalan
dan mencetuskan Zeknova…

83
00:06:24.551 --> 00:06:25.844
Kalau itu berlaku.

84
00:06:25.928 --> 00:06:29.640
kita semua kena menghadap
tribunal tentera Naib Laksamana M'Quve.

85
00:06:32.226 --> 00:06:33.727
Teruknya.

86
00:06:33.811 --> 00:06:37.022
Gundam yang setanding Gundam Merah saja
mampu menghalangnya.

87
00:06:37.106 --> 00:06:38.857
Gundam GQuuuuuuX.

88
00:06:39.358 --> 00:06:40.692
Ensain Xavier.

89
00:06:42.528 --> 00:06:46.573
Omega ialah Psycommu istimewa.
Tuan rasa saya boleh kendalikannya?

90
00:06:47.658 --> 00:06:51.453
Mereka kata awak pelajar terbaik
dalam kelas awak di Sekolah Flanagan.

91
00:06:51.537 --> 00:06:55.499
Kalau tak. saya takkan benarkan awak guna
kunci pengaktifan Psycommu yang berharga.

92
00:06:57.000 --> 00:07:00.671
Oh ya. ini misi sulit.
Awak tahu apa kena buat.

93
00:07:00.754 --> 00:07:05.384
Sekejap.
Ini pertempuran pertama saya. tuan tahu?

94
00:07:07.094 --> 00:07:08.262
Jangan risau.

95
00:07:08.929 --> 00:07:10.556
Awak Newtype. bukan?

96
00:07:19.064 --> 00:07:21.650
Ensain Xavier di dalam GQuuuuuuX.
lancarkan sekarang.

97
00:07:30.826 --> 00:07:32.494
KEADAAN ZARAH MINOVSKY
KEPEKATAN TEMPUR TAHAP 3

98
00:07:32.578 --> 00:07:34.204
Misi sulit.

99
00:07:34.788 --> 00:07:37.249
Komander percaya kita masih berperang?

100
00:07:38.000 --> 00:07:41.253
Zarah Minovsky tersebar begini.
Sesiapa pun akan perasan.

101
00:07:48.635 --> 00:07:51.138
OBJ Di Depan

102
00:08:15.078 --> 00:08:16.288
Apa ini?

103
00:08:20.626 --> 00:08:26.715
Benda ini membolehkan mobile suit awam
menggunakan senjata. Hebat juga.

104
00:08:31.470 --> 00:08:34.806
Awak tak rasa awak patut minta maaf?

105
00:08:47.027 --> 00:08:49.196
Awak pengganas?

106
00:08:53.909 --> 00:08:57.579
Tak. Saya bukan pengganas.
Itu cuma untuk Tempur Puak…

107
00:08:58.497 --> 00:09:02.626
Maksudnya. awak berlawan mobile suit
untuk dapatkan duit. Tempur Puak. bukan?

108
00:09:03.669 --> 00:09:06.546
Saya tahu perlawanan itu
popular. tapi haram.

109
00:09:14.846 --> 00:09:16.181
Aduh!

110
00:09:18.100 --> 00:09:21.186
Saya cuma hantar kunci.
Itu kerja sampingan saya.

111
00:09:21.687 --> 00:09:22.813
Kerja sampingan?

112
00:09:22.896 --> 00:09:25.148
Jadi. awak kena bayar ganti rugi!

113
00:09:35.325 --> 00:09:36.618
Ia terbang secara terbuka.

114
00:09:39.538 --> 00:09:41.290
Langsung tak menyorok.

115
00:09:42.916 --> 00:09:45.127
Betulkah itu Gundam Merah?

116
00:09:50.215 --> 00:09:52.134
Mereka tak pedulikan
isyarat gencatan senjata.

117
00:09:52.217 --> 00:09:55.762
Saya tak ada pilihan lain.
Psycommu Omega. aktifkan!

118
00:10:02.853 --> 00:10:04.062
Apa jadi?

119
00:10:16.158 --> 00:10:17.951
Vulcan kepala dan Bit!

120
00:10:18.535 --> 00:10:20.704
Ini Gundam sebenar!

121
00:10:22.372 --> 00:10:28.754
Tapi saya tak boleh buka Psycommu!
Kenapa saya tak boleh aktifkan?

122
00:10:30.339 --> 00:10:31.715
Tak guna!

123
00:10:40.807 --> 00:10:41.808
LALUAN NO. 6

124
00:10:41.892 --> 00:10:45.729
-Kurier? Hebatnya.
-Lebih kurang menonjol kalau awak pelajar.

125
00:10:47.689 --> 00:10:50.233
Tapi. polis itu tadi…

126
00:10:50.734 --> 00:10:53.987
Mereka cepat tangkap pelarian.

127
00:11:07.209 --> 00:11:09.002
Kamu bertempur di tempat begini?

128
00:11:11.254 --> 00:11:13.757
Tak ada orang waras
akan masuk Tempur Puak.

129
00:11:27.062 --> 00:11:29.064
Helo. Awak nak cepat?

130
00:11:48.834 --> 00:11:50.502
Helo?

131
00:11:55.632 --> 00:11:56.675
BUAT BAIK
DIBALAS BAIK

132
00:11:56.758 --> 00:12:00.137
Biar betul!
Kami hampir ditangkap disebabkan awak!

133
00:12:01.847 --> 00:12:06.393
Inilah dia. Annqi.
Polis kejar dia di stesen.

134
00:12:07.060 --> 00:12:08.311
Dia masih budak!

135
00:12:09.020 --> 00:12:10.272
Budak tak guna!

136
00:12:11.064 --> 00:12:13.567
Kurier tak patut dikesan polis!

137
00:12:14.067 --> 00:12:16.611
Lagipun. awak tak patut jumpa kami terus.

138
00:12:16.695 --> 00:12:19.406
Tapi bukankah ada permintaan
untuk hantar hari ini?

139
00:12:20.073 --> 00:12:22.451
Betul. Penghantaran dah dibayar.

140
00:12:23.827 --> 00:12:27.122
Awak pula siapa?

141
00:12:29.958 --> 00:12:33.962
Saya rasa pengasuh? Atau Mav.

142
00:12:34.713 --> 00:12:35.964
Mav?

143
00:12:36.882 --> 00:12:37.883
Nah.

144
00:12:38.884 --> 00:12:41.303
Saya dah sedia bertempur dengan benda ini!

145
00:12:44.514 --> 00:12:46.766
Saya rasa kamu berdua bukan kawan.

146
00:12:47.517 --> 00:12:49.936
Itu bukan uniform betul. bukan?

147
00:12:52.481 --> 00:12:54.816
Awak berminat dengan Tempur Puak?

148
00:12:57.402 --> 00:13:00.155
Awak tak patut bercakap
dengan budak begitu.

149
00:13:00.238 --> 00:13:02.073
Hei. siapa cakap awak boleh bergerak?

150
00:13:04.493 --> 00:13:06.244
Bolehkah kita bebas di angkasa?

151
00:13:09.331 --> 00:13:11.124
Bebas!

152
00:13:21.343 --> 00:13:22.594
Mobile suit!

153
00:13:23.553 --> 00:13:24.721
Dari bawah tanah!

154
00:13:32.812 --> 00:13:34.439
MOBILE SUIT GUNDAM GQUUUUUUX

155
00:13:44.407 --> 00:13:46.326
Bukankah kedua-duanya Gundam?

156
00:13:46.409 --> 00:13:47.619
Gundam?

157
00:13:47.702 --> 00:13:50.830
Mujurlah awak tak jahat sangat
sampai nak menembak di sini.

158
00:13:50.914 --> 00:13:51.915
Tapi…

159
00:13:55.418 --> 00:13:58.171
Tindak balas saya lebih baik
kalau saya ada kawalan Psycommu!

160
00:14:01.341 --> 00:14:04.803
Kenapa awak tak dengar kata kuasa saya.
Psycommu Omega?

161
00:14:05.845 --> 00:14:07.430
Kamu dah gila?

162
00:14:07.514 --> 00:14:09.224
Jangan berlawan di tempat begini!

163
00:14:11.017 --> 00:14:13.562
Awak buat apa? Tak sayang nyawa?

164
00:14:48.638 --> 00:14:49.639
AWAS

165
00:14:49.723 --> 00:14:52.559
Sistem kawalan tak berfungsi.
Mesti sebab saya terlalu paksa.

166
00:14:54.519 --> 00:14:56.271
Teruklah. MP datang.

167
00:15:07.866 --> 00:15:11.119
Komander Arraga.
yang merah itu tak dapat dikesan.

168
00:15:11.202 --> 00:15:15.832
Ada lif berdekatan yang turun
ke terowong senggara bawah tanah.

169
00:15:15.915 --> 00:15:17.834
Tuan tak tahu kalau ia di dalam bangunan.

170
00:15:27.469 --> 00:15:30.096
Raggucci. cabut bumbung
dan cari Gundam itu!

171
00:15:30.180 --> 00:15:32.182
Itu cuma bangunan haram
yang dibina pelarian!

172
00:15:32.265 --> 00:15:33.391
Baik!

173
00:15:34.684 --> 00:15:36.227
Tolong berhenti!

174
00:15:40.857 --> 00:15:41.858
Kejamnya.

175
00:15:42.859 --> 00:15:47.155
Walaupun Zeon menang perang ini.
Spacenoid takkan bebas.

176
00:15:47.947 --> 00:15:49.908
Kita akan terus merana.

177
00:15:53.453 --> 00:15:55.455
Tak guna! Sorokkan Zaku!

178
00:15:55.955 --> 00:15:57.582
Awak nak sorokkan?

179
00:15:59.584 --> 00:16:00.752
Awak tak nak lawan?

180
00:16:01.252 --> 00:16:03.380
Tak ada orang bodoh sampai nak lawan MP!

181
00:16:03.463 --> 00:16:06.883
Kami tak boleh bertempur
sebab kunci itu rosak!

182
00:16:14.641 --> 00:16:15.642
Hei!

183
00:16:19.437 --> 00:16:20.647
Aduhai.

184
00:16:21.481 --> 00:16:23.066
Biar betul Annqi.

185
00:16:23.566 --> 00:16:25.819
Macam mana nak sorokkan benda ini?

186
00:16:26.903 --> 00:16:28.571
Hei. awak buat apa?

187
00:16:28.655 --> 00:16:29.989
-Masuk ke mana?
-Apa?

188
00:16:35.578 --> 00:16:37.497
Jangan cari masalah!

189
00:16:37.580 --> 00:16:41.376
Kita kena lari. Kalau mereka jumpa kita.
tempat persembunyian kami akan terbongkar!

190
00:16:41.459 --> 00:16:42.752
Di mana nak masukkan…

191
00:16:42.836 --> 00:16:44.170
Di bawah bar hendal.

192
00:16:45.422 --> 00:16:46.673
Awak nak buat apa?

193
00:16:46.756 --> 00:16:48.717
-Saya nak lawan mereka!
-Apa?

194
00:16:51.511 --> 00:16:53.054
ZEONIC

195
00:16:58.184 --> 00:17:00.812
Mata tunggal merah. Bersenjata!

196
00:17:02.147 --> 00:17:03.314
Penjual sekerap tak guna!

197
00:17:13.450 --> 00:17:16.411
Terowong senggara lama.

198
00:17:17.495 --> 00:17:20.039
Nampak macam kedap udara.

199
00:17:20.123 --> 00:17:22.125
Bolehkah saya sembunyikannya di sini?

200
00:17:33.678 --> 00:17:35.096
Apa itu?

201
00:17:35.180 --> 00:17:37.682
Bukan yang merah.
Saya tak pernah tengok jenis itu!

202
00:17:37.766 --> 00:17:40.894
Boleh jadi itu mobile suit tak dikenali
yang menyerang sasaran.

203
00:17:40.977 --> 00:17:42.103
TENTERA ZEON
XAVIER OLIVETTE

204
00:17:42.187 --> 00:17:43.396
Sut juruterbang itu.

205
00:17:44.355 --> 00:17:47.150
Hei. kenapa Zeon menyelinap di sini?

206
00:17:47.233 --> 00:17:50.236
Tunggu! Kami sekutu Side 6!

207
00:17:51.780 --> 00:17:53.615
Jangan dekat dengan mobile suit itu!

208
00:17:53.698 --> 00:17:56.284
Berhenti! Jangan sentuh mesin ini!

209
00:18:00.079 --> 00:18:01.080
Tak guna.

210
00:18:01.164 --> 00:18:03.917
Tak mungkin kita boleh menang
dengan besi buruk ini.

211
00:18:05.919 --> 00:18:07.545
Yang itu nampak jauh lebih kuat.

212
00:18:08.379 --> 00:18:10.131
Sekejap. apa maksud awak?

213
00:18:10.715 --> 00:18:11.841
Kuat!

214
00:18:11.925 --> 00:18:13.051
Berhenti. bodoh!

215
00:18:33.404 --> 00:18:34.864
Apa saya patut buat?

216
00:18:34.948 --> 00:18:36.032
Buka kunci.

217
00:18:36.783 --> 00:18:38.117
Buka kunci?

218
00:18:38.618 --> 00:18:39.911
PENGAKTIFAN BERJAYA
BUKA KUNCI SELESAI

219
00:18:54.467 --> 00:18:56.928
Apa ini? Letak tapak tangan di sini?

220
00:19:03.017 --> 00:19:04.394
Ia bergerak!

221
00:19:05.687 --> 00:19:06.896
Kenapa ia bergerak?

222
00:19:26.165 --> 00:19:28.251
Isyarat pengaktifan
Psycommu Omega diterima!

223
00:19:28.751 --> 00:19:30.670
Bagus. Xavier!

224
00:19:31.337 --> 00:19:32.338
Ia berfungsi.

225
00:19:36.217 --> 00:19:37.427
Ia berdiri.

226
00:19:44.934 --> 00:19:46.394
Senjata. Senjata?

227
00:19:47.103 --> 00:19:48.479
Awak nak melawan?

228
00:19:54.986 --> 00:19:56.195
Tak guna!

229
00:20:00.033 --> 00:20:01.075
Alamak!

230
00:20:08.541 --> 00:20:09.626
Biar betul!

231
00:20:12.587 --> 00:20:13.671
Raggucci!

232
00:20:18.051 --> 00:20:21.346
Tak guna. Berani awak serang Mav saya!

233
00:20:24.557 --> 00:20:26.017
MEMBUKA PINTU KEDAP UDARA

234
00:20:28.102 --> 00:20:29.896
Alamak. pintu kedap udara…

235
00:20:29.979 --> 00:20:31.481
PINTU KECEMASAN

236
00:20:40.156 --> 00:20:41.574
Tak boleh berhenti!

237
00:20:44.494 --> 00:20:46.162
Amatur betul.

238
00:20:46.245 --> 00:20:48.081
Sia-sia awak melawan!

239
00:20:48.665 --> 00:20:50.249
Matilah awak di angkasa!

240
00:20:56.422 --> 00:20:58.508
Bunuh atau dibunuh!

241
00:21:09.227 --> 00:21:10.436
Apa yang berkilauan itu?

242
00:21:13.022 --> 00:21:14.107
Kira-kira.

243
00:21:17.402 --> 00:21:18.403
Siapa itu?

244
00:21:19.445 --> 00:21:22.448
Gundam Merah. Gundam tadi!

245
00:21:24.867 --> 00:21:26.619
Saya tak tahu apa yang berlaku.

246
00:21:27.286 --> 00:21:28.705
tapi saya rasa dah faham!

247
00:21:42.385 --> 00:21:43.761
Mereka pun Mav?

248
00:21:49.183 --> 00:21:50.184
Marilah!

249
00:22:09.829 --> 00:22:11.164
Saya dah kalahkan dia.

250
00:22:15.626 --> 00:22:17.462
Siapa itu?

251
00:22:19.213 --> 00:22:20.631
Mobile suit menghampiri.

252
00:22:21.132 --> 00:22:22.925
Gundam! Semakin dekat!

253
00:22:26.554 --> 00:22:28.181
Biar betul?

254
00:22:28.264 --> 00:22:31.017
-Itu bukan kapten.
-Tak pernah tengok depan-depan!

255
00:22:31.100 --> 00:22:34.228
-Tapi siapa itu?
-Ketumpatan zarah Minovsky tinggi!

256
00:22:38.232 --> 00:22:43.237
♪~

257
00:22:45.448 --> 00:22:47.617
♪ A roundabout fantasy.
anthology

258
00:22:47.742 --> 00:22:48.785
♪ Mystery & Mystery

259
00:22:48.910 --> 00:22:49.911
♪ I'm acting on instinct

260
00:22:50.036 --> 00:22:51.788
♪ The impulse that rises
to the beat of my heart

261
00:22:52.413 --> 00:22:54.332
♪ "I don't care anymore..."

262
00:23:01.047 --> 00:23:04.467
♪ I just want to know easy things

263
00:23:04.592 --> 00:23:08.137
♪ What I really wish for the stars

264
00:23:08.471 --> 00:23:11.682
♪ No more excuses for my anguish

265
00:23:11.808 --> 00:23:13.518
♪ No more. it's meaningless

266
00:23:13.643 --> 00:23:15.311
♪ What do you think?

267
00:23:15.436 --> 00:23:18.856
♪ It's like I've lost my way.

268
00:23:18.981 --> 00:23:22.610
♪ My heart is a thorn in my side.

269
00:23:23.027 --> 00:23:26.280
♪ It's just the same old thing
over and over again.

270
00:23:26.405 --> 00:23:29.283
♪ Like I'm dancing in a birdcage.

271
00:23:30.118 --> 00:23:31.786
♪ Weak and pierced
Till it's mended

272
00:23:31.911 --> 00:23:33.621
♪ Struggling and crying
And try not to disappear

273
00:23:33.746 --> 00:23:35.373
♪ It's so convenient like some magic

274
00:23:35.498 --> 00:23:37.166
♪ If you're the hero.
there's a beginning and an end

275
00:23:37.291 --> 00:23:39.252
♪ No matter what happens in the end.
it's always a happy ending

276
00:23:39.377 --> 00:23:41.295
♪ Then let me do what I want

277
00:23:41.420 --> 00:23:43.798
♪ I don't care anymore.

278
00:23:44.090 --> 00:23:45.675
♪ I fell headlong

279
00:23:45.800 --> 00:23:47.927
♪ into a zero-gravity Midnight escape

280
00:23:48.094 --> 00:23:50.847
♪ The Secret Behind the Secret.
I'm a Prisoner of that

281
00:23:51.139 --> 00:23:52.849
♪ Take it all with you

282
00:23:52.974 --> 00:23:55.101
♪ I'm celebrating life
with everything I've got

283
00:23:55.226 --> 00:23:58.604
♪ Thinking of the stars mingling together

284
00:23:58.729 --> 00:24:00.982
♪ I can't believe
someone says "I love you"

285
00:24:01.107 --> 00:24:03.568
♪ This night is all Wonder

286
00:24:03.693 --> 00:24:05.820
♪ Singing of love

287
00:24:11.033 --> 00:24:14.036
~♪

288
00:24:16.289 --> 00:24:18.416
Pada penghujung Perang Kebebasan Zeon.

289
00:24:18.499 --> 00:24:21.377
mobile suit Persekutuan. Gundam. muncul.

290
00:24:21.460 --> 00:24:25.298
dengan Char "Komet Merah"
legenda di dalamnya.

291
00:24:25.381 --> 00:24:27.300
Episod seterusnya: "Gundam Putih".

292
00:24:27.383 --> 00:24:29.177
Merah? Putih? Yang mana satu?

293
00:24:29.260 --> 00:24:30.469
GUNDAM PUTIH

294
00:24:30.553 --> 00:24:32.555
Terjemahan sari kata oleh Aizat Bahri
